    • 构造器详细资料

      • Builder

        public Builder(PerStateBytes componentLevelThresholds,
               java.util.Map<java.lang.String,PerStateBytes> packageSpecificThresholds,
               java.util.Map<java.lang.String,PerStateBytes> appCategorySpecificThresholds,
               java.util.List<IoOveruseAlertThreshold> systemWideThresholds)
        Creates a new Builder.
        参数:
        componentLevelThresholds - Component level thresholds.

        These are applied to packages that are not covered by the package specific thresholds or application category specific thresholds. For third-party component, only component level thresholds must be provided and other thresholds are not applicable.

        packageSpecificThresholds - Package specific thresholds only for system and vendor packages. NOTE: For packages that share a UID, the package name should be the shared package name because the I/O usage is aggregated for all packages under the shared UID. The shared package names should have the prefix 'shared:'.

        System component must provide package specific thresholds only for system packages.

        Vendor component must provide package specific thresholds only for vendor packages.

        appCategorySpecificThresholds - Application category specific thresholds.

        The key must be one of the ResourceOveruseConfiguration#ApplicationCategoryType constants.

        These are applied when package specific thresholds are not provided for a package and a package is covered by one of the ResourceOveruseConfiguration#ApplicationCategoryType. These thresholds must be provided only by the vendor component.

        systemWideThresholds - List of system-wide thresholds used to detect overall disk I/O overuse.

        These thresholds must be provided only by the system component.
